{"id": "1408380361104293918", "channel_id": "1408380361104293918", "type": 0, "author_id": "1362313261629964291", "author_name": "mythag_navigator", "author_bot": false, "content": "「アイギスが強すぎて勝てないよ...だれか助けて！！」\n\n調査1-13は序盤の難所です\n皆さんの攻略のコツを教えてください", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T09:20:44.529000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1408380361263550585", "filename": "Emoji_KP_F_11.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 39737, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408380361104293918/1408380361263550585/Emoji_KP_F_11.png?ex=6a33b86c&is=6a3266ec&hm=101e64caabcd5d546ad1114344f1a7eefaccd75e5d9fb07fdd9a3a6ddda2dd32&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408380361104293918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調査1-13攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1408388812958339072", "channel_id": "1408380361104293918", "type": 0, "author_id": "712132625447518249", "author_name": "zoo8849", "author_bot": false, "content": "無課金パーティーでノーデスクリアをやってみたくて、ラモンナ、ドール、オジール、ロータンの4人でやりましたが、ワンデスでのクリアでした。\nもう少し、付ける刻印にガード系かコスト関係のやつがあればよかったかも……", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T09:54:19.608000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408380361104293918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調査1-13攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1408399831373975704", "channel_id": "1408380361104293918", "type": 0, "author_id": "1319854722190151721", "author_name": "guilei0379", "author_bot": false, "content": "ひたすら防御で守って毒でアイギスのバリアごと粉砕した", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T10:38:06.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408380361104293918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調査1-13攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1408401114738458774", "channel_id": "1408380361104293918", "type": 0, "author_id": "647418640752443393", "author_name": "5cm_sergeant", "author_bot": false, "content": "多分最適解ではないです。\n下段は適当に入れてて、中央2人で高火力の攻撃を受け流しつつ、低火力の攻撃が来る際にカーシアの超次元で溜め込んだ攻撃カードを守備そっちのけで叩き込みました。", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T10:43:12.581000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1408401114365169775", "filename": "IMG_0004.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1162590, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408380361104293918/1408401114365169775/IMG_0004.png?ex=6a33cbc0&is=6a327a40&hm=dbf3d2a51afe7d35a7b40b6a131313e6691f3de7f1eaf0bed5b2eb58b8b95c65&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408380361104293918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調査1-13攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1408416236861395017", "channel_id": "1408380361104293918", "type": 0, "author_id": "279045292639387648", "author_name": "horydragon", "author_bot": false, "content": "ノーコンテニューでクリア出来たので意識した点を纏めます\n・遺物は恩恵の血は最優先で取る→毎ターン回復するため\n・刻印は力増加系をメインで取る\n・火力はロータンの傲慢かラモンナの女王の剣がメイン\n・石ころ変換は絶対に等価交換で手札に残さないようにする\n・覚醒はオジール最優先（長期戦前提で力をためる必要があるため）\n・あとドールも覚醒しておくと回復力が底上げされるので生存優先で覚醒を確保\n　┗ラモンナとロータンは優先度低めでOK\n・運が良かった部分もあるとは思うがこの辺りを意識すれば最悪1コンテニュー程度には治ると思われます", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T11:43:17.976000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-22T11:58:24.401000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 14}], "attachments": [{"id": "1408416235368218624", "filename": "IMG_0462.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 984495, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408380361104293918/1408416235368218624/IMG_0462.png?ex=6a33d9d5&is=6a328855&hm=d548e1363c779e7c30c854db37fccd9d2654f90c2c5fc2ef4bfaee8980287265&"}, {"id": "1408416235867082752", "filename": "SPOILER_IMG_0464.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1226683, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408380361104293918/1408416235867082752/SPOILER_IMG_0464.png?ex=6a33d9d5&is=6a328855&hm=f82cfc19fed78857cd0fca03d8260ff42d00efb84d54cfa2c7d9d7b32fcba59c&"}, {"id": "1408416236412473374", "filename": "IMG_0465.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 844880, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408380361104293918/1408416236412473374/IMG_0465.png?ex=6a33d9d5&is=6a328855&hm=aaa39043d0b71fd5acbf9230e3e886bc9092db66a29f19ffa3f1727b0544403a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408380361104293918", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調査1-13攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
